# ğŸ“¸ Real-Time Responsive Image Gallery

This project is a modern, responsive, and dynamic **image gallery** built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
It fetches **real-time images** from the **Unsplash API** based on categories like **nature, travel, people, animals, and technology**. 
It features a **lightbox view**, **smooth transitions**, **image navigation**, and displays **photo credits** per Unsplash guidelines.



